From 1335dd6942feb749e3ccbe1a4493458229f77a6c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Jason A. Donenfeld" <Jason@zx2c4.com>
Date: Fri, 21 Feb 2020 21:10:37 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 21/41] random: always use batched entropy for
